subject: Fix aarch64 build fail
commitMessage:
Fix aarch64 build fail

Configure cannot guess build and host variables, we must specify it.

Change-Id: Ifcfe571ba8835541c3822a89cc06186dfaef7cd2
Signed-off-by: Yury Usishchev <y.usishchev@samsung.com>

comments.message: Uploaded patch set 1.

Patch Set 1: Verified+1

This patch does not break armv7l and i586 build and enables aarch64 build.
Build results are available here: patched( https://build.tizen.org/package/show?package=krb5&project=devel%3Aarm_toolchain%3AMobile%3Atest ) and original( https://build.tizen.org/package/show?package=krb5_fail&project=devel%3Aarm_toolchain%3AMobile%3Atest )
Patch Set 1: Code-Review+2 Verified+1
Change has been successfully merged into the git repository.
